metadata.description: MATURE READERS  This is the Honey Badger. He's had his own video, commercials, and even a comic book. But Honey Badger don't care. Long as he gets to eat whenever he's not asleep, that's all that matters. Plenty of animals, people, and...things...have a problem with the Honey Badger's attitude, and they're all gonna be up in his furry grill, but when you're that badass, you don't give-well, you know.
metadata.name: Honey Badger vs. The World!
